rComments: This class is pretty easy. As long as you go to class you will pass. The teacher is not difficult at all. I'm not into English classes at all but the content in this class was pretty easy to understand. You'll do fine on the assignments as long as you follow the instructions which are pretty easy.

Nearly impossible to pay attention to and has no confidence teaching. She is NOT an easy marker, probably because she looked at this site and decided to change her marking style. Never replies to my emails and is not motivating at all. Her marking is unfair and random.

Really nice and understanding professor. Encouraged class participation and accepted all views presented. Unfortunately not very interesting and didn't really make me think. I felt like I didn't learn much from her class. Very easy class though.

So basically I had her for ENG1100 and it was great. It was such a laid back easy class , on the first day we all just stood up and introduced d ourselves. The material was easy , and she was so nice , I use to email her on a regular for help , and she was always so willing to help with everything , and if you need an extension , she gave them.

Amazing prof! I hate English and this was a mandatory course - she made it so interesting and fun! She truly knows her subject, in all its aspects. Most importantly, she was able to meet us on our level, providing class notes and tips on Blackboard. Very friendly and approachable and FAIR!!! Wide range of poems and plays covered, modern and older!!
